# AcadPulse Dashboard — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A professional React+Vite dashboard for **AcadPulse** — an early warning system for at-risk students.

## Architecture

```
src/
├── main.jsx              (entry point)
├── index.css             (global styles + design tokens)
├── App.jsx               (root component)
└── components/
    ├── Header.jsx + .css  (brand + bell + login)
    └── Dashboard.jsx + .css (3 tab cards)
```

## Key Design Decisions

| Decision | Rationale |
|----------|-----------|
| Inline SVG icons | No external deps, instant load, style with CSS |
| CSS custom properties | Easy palette changes, used across all components |
| BEM-style class naming | Professional, scalable, conflict-free |
| Gradient icon backgrounds | Each card visually distinct — blue, teal, purple |

